title: Week 7 NFL Recap, Analysis; Bears can't win with Trubisky (Football 10/21)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 7 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Eagles-Cowboys (1:00), Saints-Bears (12:45), Raiders-Packers (29:05), Vikings-Lions (39:30), 49ers-Redskins (50:25), Ravens-Seahawks (59:30), Texans-Colts (1:09:30), Chargers-Titans (1:17:30), Jags-Bengals (1:28:30), Dolphins-Bills (1:35:00), Rams-Falcons (1:37:30), and Cardinals-Giants (1:42:30).
